            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, top the <strong>toasted brioche base </strong>with a <strong>roasted pepper half</strong>, a handful of <strong>crispy 'seaweed'</strong>, a <strong>beef patty</strong>, the <strong>black bean & onion sauce </strong>and finally the <strong>toasted brioche lid</strong></p><p>Sprinkle your <strong>toasted sesame seeds</strong> over the <strong>fries</strong> and serve to the side with the <strong>remaining crispy 'seaweed'</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
